\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The University of KwaZulu-Natal is a public institution offering in a contact mode. The institution has also made an application for a Master of Arts and a Doctor of Philosophy in International Relations\line \line The Accreditation Committee decided at its meeting of 01 June 2011 to defer this programme pending the appointment of a second evaluator. \cell \pard 

